"3 cups chicken stock or low-sodium broth","3 cups water","2 cups cola, preferably GuS Dry Cola","1 1/2 cups Pinot Noir or other dry red wine","1/2 cup turbinado sugar","1/2 cup buckwheat honey or other dark honey","1/4  red wine vinegar","1/2  sweet onion, thinly sliced","1/2 cup (2 ounces) fresh ginger, thinly sliced","1  carrot, thinly sliced","5  (small) dried red chiles","1 1/2 teaspoons coriander seeds, crushed","1 1/2 teaspoons fennel seeds, crushed","1 1/2 teaspoons black peppercorns, crushed","1  bone-in smoked ham","  Red Pepper Jelly, for serving"